---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import DisciplinePage from '../../components/DisciplinePage.astro';
import '../../styles/global.css';
const related = [
  { href: '/disciplines/user-experience-design/', title: 'User Experience Design', icon: '/assets/webflow-safe/ux-design.svg' },
  { href: '/disciplines/conversie-optimalisatie-cro/', title: 'Conversie Optimalisatie (CRO)', icon: '/assets/webflow-safe/cro.svg' },
  { href: '/disciplines/crm/', title: 'Customer Relationship Management (CRM)', icon: '/assets/webflow-safe/crm.svg' },
  { href: '/disciplines/ecommerce-management/', title: 'eCommerce Management', icon: '/assets/webflow-safe/ecommerce.svg' },
  { href: '/disciplines/marketing-automation/', title: 'Marketing Automation', icon: '/assets/webflow-safe/marketing-automation.svg' },
];
---
<BaseLayout title="Fillter | Omni en Opti-channel solutions" description="Fillter is jouw partner voor Omni en Opti-channel solutions op maat.">
  <DisciplinePage
    title="Omni en Opti- channel solutions"
    icon="/assets/webflow-safe/omnichannel.svg"
    intro={[
      'Verkopen in je winkel met thuislevering? Online bestellingen afrekenen of retourneren aan de kassa van je filiaal? Klanten verwachten een naadloze omnichannel ervaring.',
      'Maar ook alle andere touchpoints waarmee en klant in contact komt moeten perfect aansluiten. Een opti-channel visie is cruciaal om te groeien als onderneming.',
    ]}
    body={[
      'In the omnichannel world, display advertising, search engines, social media, referral websites, e-mail and mobile marketing can be considered independent channels, as each can promote one-way or two-way communication.',
      'Retailers need to find ways to integrate their online and offline channels to avoid segregated campaigns. Proceed with the expectation that shoppers will swap across channels and devices, and keep promotions, messaging and language consistent across all channels and customer touch points.',
      'Omnichannel solutions also allow brands and companies to tighten supplier controls and optimise their product inventory across numerous sales channels, ensuring that the optimum stock levels are situated in each location and the channels are kept up to date with stock information.',
    ]}
    related={related}
  />
</BaseLayout>
